queries.sql: SELECT `s`.`sre_id` as `id`, `s`.`sre_nombre` as `nombre`, `s`.`sre_telefono1` as `telefono1`, `s`.`sre_telefono2` as `telefono2`, `s`.`sre_telefono3` as `telefono3`, `s`.`sre_correo` as `correo`, `s`.`sre_direccion` as `direccion`, `s`.`sre_idreg` as `idRegion`, `s`.`sre_idper_responsable` as `responsable`, `s`.`sre_estado` as `estado`, `p`.`per_nombre` as `nombre_del_responsable` FROM (`sre_sub_region`, `sre_sub_region` `s`) INNER JOIN `per_personal` `p` ON `s`.`sre_idper_responsable` = `p`.`per_id`
